messages.message:
Patch Set 1: Workflow-1

Some how I am able to reproduce this failure for single test in my environment for both functional and functional-py35 jobs. I have simply changed the response code [1] to trigger the failure and then ran single test using both functional and functional-py35 environments where I was able to see subunit.parser error.

To run single test:

tox -e functional-py35 -- -n glance.tests.functional.v2.test_images.TestImages.test_owning_tenant_can_delete_image

tox -e functional -- -n glance.tests.functional.v2.test_images.TestImages.test_owning_tenant_can_delete_image

[1] https://github.com/openstack/glance/blob/master/glance/tests/functional/v2/test_images.py#L1974
